      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 1843: loaded_ is only set on the normal path, but if loadConversations() throws after partially populating in-memory state, the next loadConversationsIfNeeded() retry can run against partially loaded state. That may duplicate work or leave inconsistent conversation state depending on which stage threw. Either make loadConversations() internally transactional/idempotent for retry, or clear/rollback the partially populated structures before propagating the failure.",
